WEBVTT

00:01.459 --> 00:04.421
[♪♪♪♪♪♪]

00:04.421 --> 00:05.713
[DOOR SHUTS]

00:05.713 --> 00:08.550
Oh, hello.

00:10.177 --> 00:12.387
Nice robe, Hef.

00:13.638 --> 00:15.140
Why'd you double lock the door?

00:15.140 --> 00:17.850
Well, I guess I just had

00:17.850 --> 00:20.687
too much cash on me.

00:26.651 --> 00:30.613
