For me and you ♪♪

03:44.891 --> 03:47.352
[♪♪♪♪♪♪]

03:48.520 --> 03:50.062
You know what?
I like it.

03:50.062 --> 03:51.898
I think it's a great idea
to treat yourself

03:51.898 --> 03:54.609
to a wild, crazy, expensive
night once in a while.

03:54.609 --> 03:56.027
