04:25.932 --> 04:31.354
And: "Oh, don't fall
for the crèème brûûlée scam."

04:32.188 --> 04:33.440
It's burnt pudding.

04:33.440 --> 04:35.733
Mm.
I don't want to hear any of that

04:35.733 --> 04:37.026
on our night out, please.

04:37.026 --> 04:37.985
You sound just like my dad.

04:37.985 --> 04:41.448
Why? Am I begging you
not to marry me?

04:41.448 --> 04:43.825
I can't believe you guys
have a whole night planned

04:43.825 --> 04:48.538
and I, the only actual fun
person, has nothing to do.

04:48.538 --> 04:52.041
Why, where's the rest
of the lollipop guild?

04:52.959 --> 04:54.836
No, no, no.
Hey, guys.

04:54.836 --> 04:55.753
Hey, guys.
No.

04:55.753 --> 04:57.297
Hey. How was your check up?

04:57.297 --> 04:58.340
All good.

04:58.340 --> 04:59.173
Yes, the doctor concurred

04:59.173 --> 05:01.468
