05:33.875 --> 05:36.168
Your iPod.

05:36.168 --> 05:40.006
[♪♪♪♪♪♪]

05:42.717 --> 05:44.719
Forty-two minutes
past our reservation.

05:44.719 --> 05:47.304
Would you relax,
we're not in a hurry.

05:47.304 --> 05:49.348
Well, they only say
that your table's not ready

05:49.348 --> 05:51.350
so you have to wait at the bar
and buy a drink.

05:51.350 --> 05:53.019
