today before I got here.

06:51.118 --> 06:52.620
Check it out.

06:52.620 --> 06:53.788
Adam's cell phone.

06:53.788 --> 06:54.622
He left it at the apartment,

06:54.622 --> 06:57.249
after all that big talk
about being responsible.

06:57.249 --> 06:58.375
Oh, that doesn't sound like him.

06:58.375 --> 07:00.336
