thing to do.

07:00.336 --> 07:01.879
Well, I guess he'll never learn.

07:01.879 --> 07:05.091
Order me a coffee.
Got you.

07:05.842 --> 07:07.802
Oh, hey, can I get a, uh...

07:07.802 --> 07:09.345
What did she want?

07:09.345 --> 07:11.723
Uh, just give me
a piece of pie.

07:12.890 --> 07:14.892
Oh, hey, genius.

07:14.892 --> 07:15.392
Hey.

07:15.226 --> 07:17.562
Get this,
I lost my cell phone.

07:17.562 --> 07:19.814
No, actually--
I'm pretty sure

07:19.814 --> 07:21.273
