07:24.736 --> 07:25.820
You did?

07:25.820 --> 07:28.322
After you promised Jen?

07:28.322 --> 07:31.868
Wow, this is gonna be
a huge problem.

07:31.868 --> 07:32.494
I know, I know.

07:32.494 --> 07:35.622
I know, she'll probably never
let me hear the end of this.

07:35.622 --> 07:36.706
Uh, what to do? What--?

07:36.706 --> 07:39.000
Okay, seriously what to do.

07:39.000 --> 07:40.627
Um, you know what?
I have an idea.

07:40.627 --> 07:42.795
Why don't you go outside
to a pay phone,

07:42.795 --> 07:43.588
and call your cell.

07:43.588 --> 07:46.340
And then if the cabbie
finds it, he'll answer it.

07:46.340 --> 07:46.924
Yeah.
Yeah.

07:46.924 --> 07:49.719
Then I get it back
before Jen knows it's gone.

07:49.719 --> 07:50.427
Yes.
All right.

07:50.427 --> 07:52.764
Oh. Wait, why can't I just
use your cell phone?

07:52.764 --> 07:54.306
You know what?
I left it at home.

07:54.306 --> 07:56.726
And it's so stupid of me.

07:56.726 --> 07:59.729
Hey, don't feel bad,
I do that too.

07:59.729 --> 08:03.149
Ah, I take great
comfort in that.

08:03.525 --> 08:04.942
Anyway thanks for the idea.

08:04.942 --> 08:06.611
No, thank you, man.

08:09.489 --> 08:13.159
Ah, ha-ha. Oh. Thank you.

08:13.159 --> 08:15.327
[EXHALES]

08:16.162 --> 08:16.996
Wait, where's my coffee?

08:16.996 --> 08:19.081
Oh, wait, that's right.
Uh, excuse me,

08:19.081 --> 08:23.044
