of ice cream on this?

08:24.128 --> 08:26.255
As a woman I don't like
to hear this word,

08:26.255 --> 08:28.633
but I have to say
you're a douche.

08:28.633 --> 08:29.175
[LAUGHING]

08:29.175 --> 08:31.177
You're gonna be
thanking this douche

08:31.177 --> 08:31.969
because Adam was just here,

08:31.969 --> 08:33.971
and he thinks he left
his cell phone in a cab.

08:33.971 --> 08:35.181
So he went to a pay phone
to call it.

08:35.181 --> 08:37.600
But he didn't leave it
in a cab, you have it there.

08:37.600 --> 08:38.976
[CELL PHONE RINGS]
Trust me.

08:38.976 --> 08:42.313
This sounds weird
but you're gonna like it.

08:42.814 --> 08:43.439
I just got a flash

08:43.439 --> 08:46.526
of what it feels like
to be on a date with you.

08:47.694 --> 08:49.862
[IN FOREIGN ACCENT]
Hello?

08:50.071 --> 08:53.449
Yes, I found this phone
in my cab.

08:53.449 --> 08:57.119
No, I didn't find
a little bag of licorice.

08:57.787 --> 08:58.788
No, listen,
if you want a phone,

08:58.788 --> 09:02.499
go meet me at The Grease Pit
on West 4th and Horatio.

09:02.499 --> 09:03.375
My name?

09:03.375 --> 09:07.797
Yes, it's Pie Al La Mode.

09:08.673 --> 09:10.424
Okay, see you there.

09:10.424 --> 09:12.176
Pie Al La Mode?
[CHUCKLES]

09:12.176 --> 09:14.095
