the address of a lesbian bar?

09:21.728 --> 09:25.732
Sometimes it's just nice to be
the prettiest one in the room.

09:27.524 --> 09:30.987
[♪♪♪♪♪♪]

09:32.321 --> 09:33.823
Uh, yes, that's it.

09:33.823 --> 09:37.619
That is the one
my husband mispronounced.

09:38.786 --> 09:41.581
That men's room
