yourself tonight.

09:48.963 --> 09:50.798
Well, when I was
talking to Ricky,

09:50.798 --> 09:54.594
my hand towel caddy, I--
I thought Audrey's right.

09:54.594 --> 09:56.763
We do deserve to live it up
once in a while.

09:56.763 --> 09:57.972
That's the spirit.

09:57.972 --> 10:00.516
