that Monopoly guy.

10:09.191 --> 10:11.778
He's got that monocle,
the top hat,

10:11.778 --> 10:14.530
the bags with the dollar
signs on them.

10:14.530 --> 10:18.159
That fictional bastard
knows how to live.

10:21.621 --> 10:23.247
