10:23.247 --> 10:24.498
[LAUGHS]

10:24.957 --> 10:27.293
That's a good one.

10:27.293 --> 10:28.002
Here you go,

10:28.002 --> 10:29.712
and there's more
where that came from.

10:29.712 --> 10:34.050
Just don't ask
where it came from.

10:36.260 --> 10:37.762
That'll play.

10:38.638 --> 10:39.138
[SIGHS]

10:39.096 --> 10:41.849
