for doing this.

10:42.224 --> 10:43.685
Thank you for suggesting it.

10:43.685 --> 10:46.520
And you really do look
very pretty tonight.

10:47.188 --> 10:50.066
To living the good life.

10:50.775 --> 10:52.443
Hey, Jeff.

10:52.443 --> 10:53.736
Oh, Stewart.

10:53.736 --> 10:55.571
You remember Audrey?

10:55.571 --> 10:57.406
Oh, my God, Lac Rouge?

10:57.406 --> 10:59.366
Ha, I guess business
