11:10.461 --> 11:13.840
Oh. Why don't you, uh,
try it for yourself?

11:13.840 --> 11:17.593
Excuse me, can I get a glass
for my compadre here?

11:17.593 --> 11:18.761
Wow, thanks.

11:18.761 --> 11:22.348
