looking at the wine list

11:30.314 --> 11:31.523
and talking about it.

11:31.523 --> 11:33.192
Put it down.

11:34.861 --> 11:36.946
Put the glass down.

11:38.823 --> 11:40.950
And walk away.

11:44.661 --> 11:47.123
