11:57.591 --> 11:59.093
Let me see that.

11:59.093 --> 12:00.427
One-fifty.

12:00.427 --> 12:02.513
One-fifty.

12:02.513 --> 12:05.808
Oh! There it is, 1500.

12:05.808 --> 12:07.977
Why didn't you bring
your reading glasses?

12:07.977 --> 12:09.478
