to your naked body.

12:13.858 --> 12:14.817
Fifteen hundred dollars?

12:14.817 --> 12:16.193
All right, look, don't panic.

12:16.193 --> 12:17.862
Let me just talk to this guy.

12:17.862 --> 12:19.655
Excuse me.

12:22.825 --> 12:26.578
