12:40.259 --> 12:40.802
Oh, really?

12:40.802 --> 12:43.554
Wouldn't you agree
that in the life of every wine,

12:43.554 --> 12:46.473
there's a moment
when it turns?

12:46.473 --> 12:49.894
Worst Law &amp; Order ever.

12:49.894 --> 12:51.645
May I?

12:51.645 --> 12:53.147
Please.

12:57.526 --> 12:59.111
