13:07.995 --> 13:11.207
[♪♪♪♪♪♪]

13:15.294 --> 13:15.794
Hey, excuse me.

13:15.794 --> 13:20.424
Uh, I'm looking for a guy
named Pie Al A Mode.

13:20.424 --> 13:20.925
A guy?

13:20.757 --> 13:24.386
No, you're-- You're
the only guy in here.

13:24.386 --> 13:26.055
Really?

13:27.098 --> 13:28.975
