13:28.975 --> 13:30.809
Her.

13:31.060 --> 13:32.895
Are you--? You sure?

13:32.895 --> 13:33.562
[MOUTHS]
Yes.

13:33.562 --> 13:36.107
So what is it? Is it--?
It's, like, ladies night?

13:36.107 --> 13:40.402
Yeah, every night is
like ladies night.

13:40.402 --> 13:41.612
Oh.

13:46.242 --> 13:49.161
Ohh.

13:49.495 --> 13:50.955
Okay, this isn't
the end of the world.

13:50.955 --> 13:53.290
I mean, our goal was to only
spend the house's money

13:53.290 --> 13:55.126
and so far,
that's all we've done.

13:55.126 --> 13:55.960
Let's just get the check.

13:55.960 --> 13:57.419
You sure you don't want
some dessert?

13:57.419 --> 13:59.671
I'd be happy to take out
a second mortgage.

13:59.671 --> 14:01.757
Excuse me, the check, please.

14:01.757 --> 14:03.842
Oh. Right away.

14:04.135 --> 14:04.760
[SIGHS]

14:04.760 --> 14:06.595
What are you using
your calculator

14:06.595 --> 14:10.641
to figure out what
the tip is on infinity?

14:10.892 --> 14:12.726
No, I'm cancelling
the hotel.

14:12.726 --> 14:14.061
It's good thinking.Yeah.

14:14.061 --> 14:16.147
You would've ruined it
for me, anyway.

14:16.147 --> 14:18.107
What are you talking about?
Oh, come on.

14:18.107 --> 14:20.317
We'd have to pay
for the hotel with our money.

14:20.317 --> 14:22.528
You had a hard enough time
enjoying yourself

14:22.528 --> 14:24.071
when it was the house's money.

14:24.071 --> 14:25.990
Reservations, please.

14:25.990 --> 14:27.033
Just like my dad.

14:27.033 --> 14:28.492
I am not like your dad.
Oh, please.

14:28.492 --> 14:30.661
I'd say you were two sides
of the same coin,

14:30.661 --> 14:31.954
but I'm afraid you'd accuse me

14:31.954 --> 14:33.915
of wasting that coin
on a metaphor.

14:33.915 --> 14:37.418
Yes, we need to cancel
a reservation for tonight.

14:37.418 --> 14:37.960
Hang up.

14:37.960 --> 14:39.420
What?
We're not cancelling.

14:39.420 --> 14:40.296
We're going to that hotel.

14:40.296 --> 14:41.881
You don't have to do this
to prove a point.

14:41.881 --> 14:45.301
I'm not. I'm doing it
to treat myself to some luxury.

14:45.301 --> 14:48.595
Come along if you think
you can handle it.

14:48.595 --> 14:51.348
Oh, I can handle it.

14:51.348 --> 14:52.141
We're on our way.

14:52.141 --> 14:54.476
I will be loving
that hotel.

14:54.476 --> 14:55.769
Not as much as me.

14:55.769 --> 14:58.564
A-ha. We'll see.
Yes, we will see.

14:58.564 --> 15:00.107
Mm-hm.

15:01.067 --> 15:03.610
Uh, okay, not so bad.

15:05.612 --> 15:07.323
Oh.

15:07.698 --> 15:10.659
Well, see, he did take off that
sip.

15:12.161 --> 15:15.789
[♪♪♪♪♪♪]

15:15.789 --> 15:16.790
Come on. Wait, wait, wait.

15:16.790 --> 15:17.917
Why are we bailing Adam out?

15:17.917 --> 15:18.792
Let's screw with him some more.

15:18.792 --> 15:21.087
No, your plan didn't work,
he didn't call.

15:21.087 --> 15:24.131
No, but the dope probably lost
his dialing finger.

15:24.131 --> 15:26.258
Look, he's been in there
for two hours,

15:26.258 --> 15:27.759
he's suffered enough.

15:27.759 --> 15:30.679
[SOFT CELL'S "TAINTED LOVE"
PLAYING OVER SPEAKERS]

15:30.679 --> 15:31.931
♪♪ Oh, oh, ohh ♪♪

15:31.931 --> 15:34.391
♪♪ Tainted love ♪♪

15:34.391 --> 15:35.309
Oh, my God.

15:35.309 --> 15:36.893
♪♪ Now I know I've got to ♪♪

15:36.893 --> 15:37.811
RUSSELL: I've got some bad news.

15:37.811 --> 15:41.941
Your dude's gone lesbo.
♪♪ Run away, I've got to ♪♪

15:41.941 --> 15:42.858
♪♪ Get away ♪♪

15:42.858 --> 15:44.693
♪♪ You don't really want it ♪♪

15:44.693 --> 15:46.528
Hey, Russell, Jen!

15:46.528 --> 15:48.530
Hey, hold on,
I'll be right down.

15:48.530 --> 15:49.115
[GIRLS CHEERING]

15:49.115 --> 15:52.994
♪♪ You need someone
To hold you tight ♪♪

15:52.994 --> 15:55.162
♪♪ And you'll think love
Is to pray ♪♪

15:55.162 --> 15:58.540
All right, ladies,
one for four, not bad.

15:59.125 --> 16:00.917
What are you guys
doing here?

16:00.917 --> 16:01.627
Uh...

16:01.627 --> 16:03.670
It was Russell's idea.

16:04.088 --> 16:08.592
Oh. Oh, so you pretended
to be Pie Al A Mode.

16:10.261 --> 16:12.388
Oh, I just got that.

16:12.888 --> 16:14.181
I actually found your phone.

16:14.181 --> 16:15.349
So, what's the point
of all this?

16:15.349 --> 16:17.851
We were trying to teach you
a lesson about your phone.

16:17.851 --> 16:19.770
Button up your shirt,
let's get out of here.

16:19.770 --> 16:21.981
Now, see?
That's just a waste.

16:21.981 --> 16:23.440
Adam, you're not
leaving, are you?

16:23.440 --> 16:25.609
Because we got another
round coming.

16:25.609 --> 16:26.152
Yeah.

16:26.152 --> 16:27.944
Why do they
love you so much?

16:27.944 --> 16:28.862
Well, because a while ago

16:28.862 --> 16:31.823
Melanie here started
choking on some nuts.

16:31.823 --> 16:34.326
[CHUCKLES]
Ironic.

16:34.326 --> 16:35.911
Why is that ironic?

16:36.537 --> 16:38.664
Because it's not.

16:38.664 --> 16:41.958
Anyway, I swung into action,
dove across the bar,

16:41.958 --> 16:42.959
and gave her the Heimlich.

16:42.959 --> 16:45.087
He saved her life.
Mm-hm.

16:45.712 --> 16:47.923
Honey, that is impressive.
Isn't it?

16:47.923 --> 16:51.427
There was an emergency
and I came to the rescue.

16:51.427 --> 16:53.095
All right, I get it.

16:53.095 --> 16:56.557
You will be my "in case of
emergency" person from now on.

16:56.557 --> 16:57.308
Thank you.

16:57.308 --> 17:00.227
And you may
or may not regret it.

17:00.227 --> 17:01.562
All right, let's get out of
here.

17:01.562 --> 17:03.730
I feel like a sausage
in a vegetarian restaurant.

17:03.730 --> 17:06.233
Hey, Russell,
this place is kind of fun.

17:06.233 --> 17:07.734
Come on, one drink.

17:07.734 --> 17:09.153
I guess we could have the one.

17:09.153 --> 17:11.155
All right, all right.

17:11.322 --> 17:12.614
Jen?

17:13.032 --> 17:14.408
Patty Miller, from college.

17:14.408 --> 17:17.119
Remember spring break,
we shared that cabin?

17:17.119 --> 17:19.621
♪♪ Tainted love... ♪♪

17:20.622 --> 17:21.332
Hey, there.

17:21.332 --> 17:23.459
That's crazy.
How about that?

17:23.459 --> 17:25.752
Running into someone
you know here. That's--

17:25.752 --> 17:27.921
It's really good to see you.

17:27.921 --> 17:29.673
We gotta go.

17:29.673 --> 17:32.468
Hey. What did you guys
do in the cabin?

17:32.468 --> 17:34.595
Hi. Was there a Jacuzzi?

17:34.595 --> 17:35.721
Hey! Was there a Jacuzzi?

17:35.721 --> 17:38.182
You wanna reenact it?
Don't leave.

17:38.182 --> 17:38.974
Hey!

17:38.974 --> 17:41.227
[♪♪♪♪♪♪]

17:41.227 --> 17:44.771
Oh, that champagne
in the limo was tasty.

17:44.771 --> 17:47.774
Yeah? Glad you liked it,
because it wasn't included.

17:47.774 --> 17:48.525
It's a lot extra.

17:48.525 --> 17:51.112
Oh, well, then it's a thing
you were in the limo

17:51.112 --> 17:53.697
with me instead of your dad.

17:53.697 --> 17:55.074
May I help you?

17:55.074 --> 17:56.742
Reservation under Bingham.

17:56.742 --> 17:57.659
[TYPING]

17:57.659 --> 17:58.494
Ah, yes, here we are.

17:58.494 --> 18:00.454
Should I put the balance
on the same credit card?

18:00.454 --> 18:03.124
Balance? No, I thought
I already paid for the room.

18:03.124 --> 18:05.917
Uh, you paid a deposit of $350.

18:05.917 --> 18:09.171
That is half the price
of the room.
Half?

18:09.588 --> 18:12.383
Is that a problem for you?

18:12.383 --> 18:12.966
No.

18:12.966 --> 18:15.261
I think that sounds
like a fair price for

18:15.261 --> 18:19.055
"an economy double with
obstructed view of the street."

18:19.055 --> 18:20.724
Excellent.
Wait a minute.

18:20.724 --> 18:22.518
Oh, is that
a problem for you?

18:22.518 --> 18:23.477
Sure is.

18:23.477 --> 18:25.061
I don't want an obstructed view.

18:25.061 --> 18:27.356
How much for a room
overlooking the Park?

18:27.356 --> 18:29.858
Ah! Sounds good to me.

18:29.858 --> 18:32.694
That is this one
right here, sir.
Wow.

18:32.694 --> 18:33.195
Are you saying

18:33.195 --> 18:35.114
that we should settle
for an obstructed view,

18:35.114 --> 18:37.574
because we're only gonna
be here for 12 hours?

18:37.574 --> 18:39.410
Actually, our check-out
time is--

18:39.410 --> 18:41.328
Nine hours?
No.

18:41.328 --> 18:44.790
I was just noticing that if we
upgrade to the Club Level,

18:44.790 --> 18:46.750
we'll be able to enjoy
a private butler.

18:46.750 --> 18:50.296
Unless you think
that's too much.

18:50.296 --> 18:52.088
Butler us.

18:53.132 --> 18:55.176
And may I arrange
for some refreshments

18:55.176 --> 18:56.260
to be sent up to your suite?

18:56.260 --> 18:58.137
Sure. How about
some caviar?

18:58.137 --> 19:00.389
Great.
And some lobster.

19:00.389 --> 19:01.473
And an in-room massage.

19:01.473 --> 19:03.142
Oh, and some flowers.
And a shoe shine.

19:03.142 --> 19:05.561
Actually, we have
a complimentary shoe shine.

19:05.561 --> 19:07.020
Then I don't want it.

19:07.020 --> 19:08.564
Just more caviar.

19:08.564 --> 19:09.690
All right. Excellent.

19:09.690 --> 19:12.568
And Vincent will show you
to your suite.

19:12.568 --> 19:13.235
Great.

19:13.235 --> 19:13.944
[ELEVATOR BELL CHIMES]

19:13.944 --> 19:16.112
[CLEARS THROAT]
I can't wait to see the view.

19:16.112 --> 19:18.324
I can't wait
to shovel down some caviar.

19:18.324 --> 19:20.826
I am loving this.
Not as much as me.

19:20.826 --> 19:21.827
Club level, Vincent.

19:21.827 --> 19:24.455
No turning back now.

19:24.455 --> 19:27.040
[ELEVATOR BELL CHIMES]

19:27.958 --> 19:29.168
[ELEVATOR BELL CHIMES]

19:29.168 --> 19:31.462
Ah! I can't do this.
Oh, thank God.

19:31.462 --> 19:33.922
[♪♪♪♪♪♪]

19:35.966 --> 19:38.927
[♪♪♪♪♪♪]

19:39.220 --> 19:40.887
All right, tell me honestly,

19:40.887 --> 19:41.555
if I hadn't stop us,

19:41.555 --> 19:43.432
would you have gone
through with it?

19:43.432 --> 19:45.100
I would have gone all the way.

19:45.100 --> 19:46.017
Really?

19:46.017 --> 19:47.394
All the way to our suite,

19:47.394 --> 19:49.730
and then I would have
faked a heart attack.

19:49.730 --> 19:52.191
[LAUGHING]

19:52.191 --> 19:54.193
Oh, we have a message.

19:54.193 --> 19:55.652
MAN:
Hey, sweetheart, it's your dad.

19:55.652 --> 19:58.822
Just wanted you to know we
returned that fancy computer.

19:58.822 --> 20:00.991
We'll be sending you
the money back.

20:00.991 --> 20:03.619
Okay, my minute's
almost up, gotta go.

20:03.619 --> 20:04.953
[BEEPS]

20:04.953 --> 20:07.373
Well, he returned it.

20:07.373 --> 20:08.874
No surprise there.

20:08.874 --> 20:11.001
Well, look, your dad
is a good man.

20:11.001 --> 20:12.378
He and your mom sacrificed

20:12.378 --> 20:14.588
so that you could have
nice things,

20:14.588 --> 20:15.922
go to college.

20:15.922 --> 20:18.091
And meet me.

20:18.592 --> 20:19.760
[CHUCKLES]
I know.

20:19.760 --> 20:21.262
And the part of the reason
I love you

20:21.262 --> 20:23.222
is because you're
a little like him.

20:23.222 --> 20:24.890
Maybe a little bit.

20:24.890 --> 20:26.558
And, hey, since he returned
the laptop,

20:26.558 --> 20:28.602
we got another check
coming our way.

20:28.602 --> 20:29.520
More house money.

20:29.520 --> 20:31.146
Yeah, maybe this time

20:31.146 --> 20:33.106
we should put it
somewhere safe.

20:33.106 --> 20:34.483
Agreed.

20:34.483 --> 20:36.318
I'll go get the glue stick.

20:37.903 --> 20:40.531
[♪♪♪♪♪♪]

20:44.117 --> 20:46.828
[♪♪♪♪♪♪]
